## Build

```
# very first time, add base application from smart-design-platform (ie. desinger)
$ yarn add @things-factory/desinger
```

```
# install node_modules
$ yarn install
# data migration in development mode
$ yarn run migration --mode=development
# run application (@things-factory/{{ name }}) in development mode
$ DEBUG=sdp:* yarn run serve:dev
```

```
# data migration in production mode
$ yarn run migration --mode=production
# build application (server module)
$ yarn build
# build application (client module)
$ yarn build:client
# run application (@sdp/{{ name }}) in production mode
$ yarn run serve
```

